N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4820.33 - Rental payment due

State Regulations

The rent charged a licensed authorized organization, for
use of premises in which to conduct bingo, shall be paid in full by check
within 48 hours after the conclusion of each bingo occasion. Notes
